      <title>特朗普向拒绝亲自上班的联邦雇员提供买断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-offers-buyouts-to-federal-workers-who-want-to-work-from-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统正在向那些不愿意遵从他要求重返办公室的机构员工提供买断待遇，他希望在第二任期内重组联邦劳动力队伍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-offers-buyouts-to-federal-workers-who-want-to-work-from-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 23:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度股市暴跌 6000 亿美元后投资者关注预算救济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/india-budget-guide-traders-seek-spending-boost-after-600-billion-stock-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度投资者希望联邦预算能采取果断措施，提振低迷的消费，恢复人们对印度股市的信心。过去一个月，印度股市市值已缩水逾 6000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/india-budget-guide-traders-seek-spending-boost-after-600-billion-stock-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支出暂停令引发混乱，随后遭阻挠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-spending-halt-spawns-day-of-chaos-before-getting-blocked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统上任时承诺要振兴华盛顿。混乱的 24 小时让我们看到了特朗普的最终结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-spending-halt-spawns-day-of-chaos-before-getting-blocked</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 22:58:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将在全面制裁措施中提议禁止俄罗斯铝产品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/eu-to-propose-russian-aluminum-ban-in-sweeping-sanctions-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在克里姆林宫入侵乌克兰三周年之际，欧盟提议分阶段禁止进口俄罗斯铝，作为广泛制裁措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/eu-to-propose-russian-aluminum-ban-in-sweeping-sanctions-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 22:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯最终将拿出重振英国经济的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/reeves-to-finally-show-her-cards-with-plan-to-revive-uk-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯承诺将通过放开新的基础设施项目来“进一步加快”英国经济发展，在财政大臣任期经历艰难开局后，她希望吸引投资者并赢回商业支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/reeves-to-finally-show-her-cards-with-plan-to-revive-uk-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普冻结拨款的举措被法官暂时叫停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-freeze-on-grant-funding-temporarily-halted-by-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿的一名联邦法官暂时阻止特朗普政府执行一项新指令，即暂停向全国一系列项目发放联邦补助、贷款和其他援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-freeze-on-grant-funding-temporarily-halted-by-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 21:59:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普因禁止跨性别军人服兵役遭美国军队起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-sued-by-transgender-troops-over-new-military-service-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[六名美国军人起诉唐纳德·特朗普总统，指控他发布行政命令禁止跨性别者参军，此举为 LGBTQ 权利的新一轮斗争埋下了伏笔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-sued-by-transgender-troops-over-new-military-service-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 19:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂停发放联邦资金威胁各州财政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/nyc-to-san-francisco-face-havoc-from-trump-s-federal-aid-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的联邦资金暂停令流向各州、各市和其他地方政府的超过 1 万亿美元的资金面临风险，从交通基础设施到住房项目等一切都面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/nyc-to-san-francisco-face-havoc-from-trump-s-federal-aid-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 17:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 展示了中国应对美国芯片冲击的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/deepseek-shows-china-playbook-to-deal-an-even-bigger-shock-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DeepSeek 新 AI 模型的成功表明，面对美国的出口限制，中国最终可能实现更大的技术突破：生产自己的尖端芯片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/deepseek-shows-china-playbook-to-deal-an-even-bigger-shock-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 09:10:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
